      <originalsloc>
        <head>Location of Originals</head>
        <p>The original records of the Woodlawn Housekeeping Association, the Sherwood Hall Sunday School, and the Woodlawn Literary Association are in the Virginia Room of the Fairfax City Regional Library.  This manuscript collection contains photocopies of all of the above mentioned records.</p>
      </originalsloc>
